      <section id="faq">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>FAQ</h2>
          <h3>Common questions from prospective customers.</h3>
          <ul class="faq-list">
            <li>
              <div class="faq-q">Why subscription instead of per-scenario pricing?</div>
              <div class="faq-a">Safety teams don't want a one-time pile of clips &mdash; they want a library that grows continuously as their safety case evolves. Subscription aligns our incentives with yours: we make money when the library gets more useful to you over time, not by selling each new scenario individually. It also lets us amortize site capex across your subscription term rather than tax you for each capture.</div>
